title: Exclusive Video: These Grandfathered Bloopers Will Make Your Day
text:
John Stamos and Josh Peck, Grandfathered | Photo Credits: John P. Fleenor/FOX John Stamos and Josh Peck, Grandfathered | Photo Credits: John P. Fleenor/FOX Exclusive Video: These Grandfathered Bloopers Will Make Your Day 1 / 1 Back to Gallery 
There is a pair of babies on the Grandfathered set, but judging from this exclusive blooper reel, the grown-ups might be the ones who break the most. 
You can place some of the blame on John Stamos , who fails to silence his phone during a scene. Looks like he could use a pep talk from Coach Taylor . 
Check out the bloopers below. Grandfathered airs Tuesdays at 8/7c on Fox.
